{"tid":1418450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我發夢遊走左係荃灣各條防線 有問題就要指出！","createTime":"2019-08-05T18:45:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T00:38:40.000Z","uid":20989,"like":51,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"4a9ee5be3a2e9f91a4f69d430bbc40f0eb4ac796","tid":1418450,"uid":20989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:45:53.000Z","msg":"1. <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">請勿濫用be water</span></span><br />\n今日荃灣集會 好多係荃灣人 好多人事前已經計劃好哂點樣利用屋企優勢<br />\n今日遊走期間 聽到前線竟然有人話轉場 討論結果仲竟然係轉撚到去「金鐘」？<br />\n之後轉「葵芳」仲要係話「一齊坐地鐵」去<br />\n<br />\n想講 好多荃灣人 包括我 期待既係「荃灣集會」 <br />\n你要遊擊係可以 避狗都可以 但麻煩保持係「步兵」行動範圍 比盡只能去到大窩口！<br />\n<br />\n2.<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「狼來了」</span></span><br />\n我明有好多手足心急 想將個新行動目標傳開去 又唔想浪費時間解釋<br />\n但請注意返狼來了既後果 請勿濫用「有狗黎緊」、「準備比人圍喇」既謊言去欺騙同伴散水/轉場<br />\n今日多次係明顯警力不足既安全情況 未有防暴出現既情況下自行解除防線<br />\n我今日係帶住望遠鏡發夢既 我好清楚邊d人講大話<br />\n如果你有新行動 請以理服人 唔好講大話！<br />\n<br />\n3.<span style=\"color: red;\">勿過份分散</span><br />\n荃灣不同於港島有不反對通知書下封哂路 可以一條馬路行哂金鐘灣仔中環各主要區域 <br />\n荃灣人多車多 又多窄巷 今日仲出埋黑社會<br />\n分散左就好難再互相支援 要注意防線之間既互相支援同連接<br />\n<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: red;\">黑社會</span><br />\n對方出刀既話 真係要避一避<br />\n但都記住要保護好周圍同伴 <br />\n唔好顧住自己走佬  推撞其他手足害佢地受傷"},{"pid":"565a3a66b2b7ee2375ac13b74de132a2f4d20855","tid":1418450,"uid":20989,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:46:32.000Z","msg":"講完要檢討既野 都要讚一讚<br />\n荃灣人好波<br />\n今日封路 堵塞交通之快 真係前所未見 話黎就黎！"},{"pid":"22111a0984c2d1fa7d3ab6e203f6b96f72968310","tid":1418450,"uid":20989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:46:52.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"026ea69565b8546950582e051a4892041c8ded66","tid":1418450,"uid":20989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:47:05.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"92299848154d9a860070ad16ed60f4e843580a9b","tid":1418450,"uid":20989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:49:06.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"400a2bed2b40a8d48a54d611db96ad838fe60356","tid":1418450,"uid":264811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:49:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df3421ab8cbb661d60c097066eb88b24c540f6bc","tid":1418450,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:50:52.000Z","msg":"推實用POST<br />\n<br />\n===============<br />\n屌你老味，今日全港大戰緊有時間上連登開風向ＰＯＳＴ嘅都知咩人啦吓話？？？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dxqHdS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dxqHdS</a>"},{"pid":"a9a06e835dc2e07322fe53ea646a39df7a61bc7f","tid":1418450,"uid":20989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92299848154d9a860070ad16ed60f4e843580a9b","tid":1418450,"uid":20989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:49:06.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:52:26.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"c50c82981dc62d09b555e3567edeae72cc03a2b2","tid":1418450,"uid":135867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:52:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNOxBrP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNOxBrP.gif&h=672c8b5c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bDJNqkb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbDJNqkb.gif&h=27f2be48&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n行過想拉就拉"},{"pid":"fac8db71a4b8114c8d27cb1325230ea04631c902","tid":1418450,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:52:55.000Z","msg":"建議］ p牌正負評顯示<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dwROzT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dwROzT</a>"},{"pid":"6ffefdde8498f8cea8b246f9299f7df8779f6d47","tid":1418450,"uid":56637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:54:01.000Z","msg":"荃灣好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02e950619ce791a7333ad2d86f268978554a6582","tid":1418450,"uid":20989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:54:36.000Z","msg":"請推比各位荃灣義士同軍師們睇到<br />\n唔好再犯下同樣既錯<br />\n今日結果係大量防線係冇警察清場下自行解散<br />\n<br />\n有人決定轉地方後 人數更加大幅下滑 支援亦極慢"},{"pid":"6dae2958d800f9ea8ab3a7bbc08ae1eb40506422","tid":1418450,"uid":139407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:56:04.000Z","msg":"push!荃灣人表示支持"},{"pid":"7d11614f0e686a29cfe3ca156a5e75e90e36c7ad","tid":1418450,"uid":102185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:56:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96d5a516aa49c9bceb320b1bf68fd22bd7914273","tid":1418450,"uid":20989,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:58:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">講漏極重要 full gear!</span><br />\n荃灣請準備好full gear 唔係指對警用既裝備<br />\n而係對黑社會用既防具！<br />\n好多人以為荃灣一定和理非 <br />\n完全冇人整盾牌 亦冇人自帶球類運動用品<br />\n保護自己 帶齊「保護性命」既防具<br />\n黑社會唔同黑警 佢地有殺死你然後去坐監既覺悟"},{"pid":"1a0553d0b3a0dbbf0cea8529a5d7124973993d0d","tid":1418450,"uid":246506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:59:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位手足留意此人 係地鐵站偷拍手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418451\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418451</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"29818a97646b0ce777b062efbb1db04296c0fc86","tid":1418450,"uid":20989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:00:41.000Z","msg":"光復荃灣 要做正確既選擇<br />\n請勿放棄任何選擇留守既伙伴 包括你既跨區轉場"},{"pid":"fcb27940463caba1445be0890411330e0047d912","tid":1418450,"uid":20989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:04:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5399c1385027a7cd850da45d5c1b1670c452984","tid":1418450,"uid":110687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:06:12.000Z","msg":"真係無時間再睇tg同谷入面嘅人太雜<br />\n只可以靠天橋/現場哨兵手足<br />\n放料時，請試著用大聲公說<br />\n時地人事 起碼要有兩樣<br />\n單單一句「有狗啊」只會引起不必要嘅恐慌"},{"pid":"48e5a7984d2cc5d622f4b978f36bbd728b4c1261","tid":1418450,"uid":73617,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:09:31.000Z","msg":"今日太過新手村feel <br />\n我都好幾次呆左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最尾新界南清場我從來，從來未見過全部人散得咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb1e7800f1eb5e50894a6e3d70ba4d77556d2556","tid":1418450,"uid":62152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:10:21.000Z","msg":"荃灣只要做好哨站部分<br />\n每個站位既人有溝通方法e.g. TG<br />\n呢度其實易散易聚<br />\n散水黎講可以青山公路落大窩口<br />\n可以德士古道果邊去海濱或者去葵盛<br />\n再唔係又可以過返楊屋道撚狗<br />\n封路影響力又大<br />\n大到連黑社會都出撚埋 雖然本身都有一班"},{"pid":"578c19e0c0c5a3b288a7a21b210fc1a6b6fa5292","tid":1418450,"uid":20989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:11:48.000Z","msg":"荃灣 有黃有毒有賭 雞毒麻雀館齊哂<br />\n黑社會一定多 請勿入窄巷 留係大路 <br />\n出事起馬有人幫你叫白車/比記者拍低"},{"pid":"39a4d233befb117720e756a50ad61071e94f961f","tid":1418450,"uid":144883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:12:43.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命！"},{"pid":"adad10c4425da1c5363a72e17c07e15d95575ac8","tid":1418450,"uid":20989,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:13:50.000Z","msg":"同埋對街坊好少少 講緊唔係刻意影人大頭個d<br />\n同佢解釋下發生咩事<br />\n點解唔希望佢影相<br />\n<br />\n利申係橋比個藍絲大叔影大頭 呢d我先趕走佢"},{"pid":"7ee35834fb5b52da8aea5555c5774bbe08fea2c0","tid":1418450,"uid":33418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:14:14.000Z","msg":"荃葵青人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}